{"tid":2419262,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實啲餐廳杯凍華田沖好少少係唔係就會破產執笠？","createTime":"2021-02-23T08:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T09:33:39.000Z","uid":321771,"like":44,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d34400dba4ff3bb30433525b9c282f95310637c9","tid":2419262,"uid":321771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:14:59.000Z","msg":"其實啲餐廳杯凍華田沖好少少係唔係就會破產執笠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落多一羹粉￼佢老婆仔女係唔係就要賣落火坑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n足料少少有返味道佢老闆係唔係就要賣樓賣腎賣屎眼填返條華田數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母成撚日叫杯華田好似上一手飲完華田無洗乾淨隻杯就用嚟裝水咁，不如我煲返熱佢浸餐具啦屌，畜牲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e480ac60f01867b7a33df3fa45b758c168d88a9f","tid":2419262,"uid":217641,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4b70404733e5f8180821ebf896b0f127b1a437","tid":2419262,"uid":228143,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:18:16.000Z","msg":"華田成本最貴嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eebc82ccc8640ad73fd4685fe3917128b81d27b","tid":2419262,"uid":37719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:18:58.000Z","msg":"Hoball"},{"pid":"8697ac7c44c9dbd5f554af