aces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係咁諗，反正啲野又唔係我。<br />\n粉就落兩大羹，奶啊蜜啊全部倒勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老闆娘有時見到會叫我唔好咁重手，我就應佢：哦！好！下次！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e31419c1de528bcbed89cac1afbdb9cd7859c5","tid":2419262,"uid":330480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b704e73a4766a67afd8b79bb1ac58199144b8503","tid":2419262,"uid":78513,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:28:19.000Z","msg":"細路仔先飲華田<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:41:36.000Z","msg":"其實沖得夠味嘅華田好好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再溝啲好立克都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e726fdf1a1309d18b57f8a37893c7765d6158445","tid":2419262,"uid":375135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8697ac7c44c9dbd5f554aff8997b7943c2228679","tid":2419262,"uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:19:14.000Z","msg":"華田  貴過其他飲品好多<br />\n<br />\n基本上叫華田間餐廳冇得賺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:43:30.000Z","msg":"谷古呢？"},{"pid":"6045901af2ac949403aa7644d174523eb2b64e74","tid":2419262,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7532fe4dc8f69ffd587d02289f248bacab5a2dca","tid":2419262,"uid":226466,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:49:07.000Z","msg":"有錢人先飲得起足料華田<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似窮人食碗仔翅 有錢人食魚翅咁"},{"pid":"d1ee7eaf48ee77efb5fdae7791e8d94fe723eb2b","tid":2419262,"uid":387588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d34400dba4ff3bb30433525b9c282f95310637c9","tid":2419262,"uid":321771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:14:59.000Z","msg":"其實啲餐廳杯凍華田沖好少少係唔係就會破